Package com.irurueta.navigation.gnss

Class GNSSMeasurementsGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.irurueta.navigation.gnss.GNSSMeasurementsGenerator
  • public class GNSSMeasurementsGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Generates satellite GNSS measurement data. This implementation is based on the equations defined in "Principles of GNSS, Inertial, and Multisensor Integrated Navigation Systems, Second Edition" and on the companion software available at: https://github.com/ymjdz/MATLAB-Codes/blob/master/Generate_GNSS_measurements.m

        config - GNSS configuration parameters.

        a new GNSS measurement.
